course_description: This course is an introduction to the rules and skills necessary to play tennis. Emphasis in instruction is on the serve, return of serve, ground strokes and net play. Game management, scoring and competition (singles and doubles) as also covered.
prerequisites: Students completing PE 273 or equivalent cannot enroll for PE 173. For concerns, please contact the Physical Education department.
